title: DietMP3 4.03.00
description:
This lite application called DietMP3 can make your mp3 files to be smaller by compressing it a bit more or changing some settings on them.

You can choose the files you want to be on diet and DietMP3 will give you an stunning result, because it can make your files to be around half the size they used to be.

The size and the quality of the output files depend on the quality you want, the player you use and if you want the output files to be stereo or not.

Once you have decided those parameters, just press Start Diet and DietMP3 will do the rest for you and will surprise you wth your new files stored in the output folder you selected.
